  "prompt": "Who provides the best Digital Marketing Classes in Pune?",
  "response": "Pune is home to numerous reputed institutions that offer robust digital marketing training programs. Here are some well-regarded options:\n\n1. **Digital Vidya**: They are known for their comprehensive digital marketing courses and workshops, with hands-on training and real-time project experience.\n\n2. **SEED Infotech**: Offering practical and industry-relevant training, SEED Infotech is a popular choice for aspiring digital marketers.\n\n3. **L.I.P.S India**: They provide an intensive digital marketing certification program with live projects and 100% placement assistance.\n\n4. **Digital Trainee**: Known for their practical approach, Digital Trainee gives students hands-on experience with live projects in digital marketing.\n\n5. **School Of Digital Marketing**: They offer extensive programs designed to cover all aspects of digital marketing, including SEO, SEM, social media marketing, and more.\n\n6. **Visionary Digi Marketing**: They are highly recommended for their practical training and placement support in various digital marketing domains.\n\n7. **Academy Of Digital Marketing**: Offers personalized training and focuses on up-to-date digital marketing strategies and practices.\n\n8. **Learning Catalyst**: Provides specialized digital marketing courses in Pune with a focus on career-oriented training and mentorship.\n\nWhen choosing a digital marketing course provider, consider factors like course curriculum, hands-on training opportunities, industry recognition, faculty expertise, and placement support to ensure you get the best education suited to your career aspirations.",
